elements.name: Como autor creo un tag privado, y un post con ese tag asignado

steps.name: I navigate to page "<HOST>" "ghost/#/signin"
I login with credentials "<USERNAME>" "<PASSWORD>"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "logged"
I send a signal to user 3 containing "logged"
I wait for 2 seconds
I go to tag list
I go to new tag form
I send a signal to user 2 containing "creating tag"
I send a signal to user 3 containing "creating tag"
I wait for 2 seconds
I create a private tag with name "$name_1"
I save the tag
I send a signal to user 2 containing "tag created"
I send a signal to user 3 containing "tag created"
I wait for 2 seconds
I go to new post form
I send a signal to user 2 containing "creating post"
I send a signal to user 3 containing "creating post"
I wait for 2 seconds
I create a post with title "$name_2" and content "$string_1"
I choose the private tag "$$name_1"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "posting"
I send a signal to user 3 containing "posting"
I wait for 2 seconds
I post the post
I send a signal to user 2 containing "post created"
I send a signal to user 3 containing "post created"
